Usage: MIST_cmd.py map [OPTIONS]

  - map mNGS reads against reference genomes

Options:
  -p, --thread INTEGER     Number of threads for Bowtie2
  -i, --indexpath PATH     input folder of reference index files
  -U, --single_end PATH    input single-end fq file
